    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n8522" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">στεῦμαι</span></b> , <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">στεῦται</span>, ipf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">στεῦτο</span>:
          denotes the expression of a wish by a gesture, <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">have the
            appearance, make as if</span>, foll. by inf., regularly the fut.,
          once  aor., ‘pretends to have heard,’ <i><span class="en">Od. 17.525</span></i>; <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">διψά̄ων</span>, ‘stood as if thirsty,’ <i><span class="en">Od. 11.584</span></i>; in general, <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">engage, threaten,
            promise</span>, <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">τινί</span>, <i><span class="en">Il. 5.832</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
